content: I love this app! It is perfect for my 4 years old. At first I downleaded the free version and decided to do the in app purchase but was I was disappointed because i could not share the app to my family library to intall it on all devices. I contacted RosiMosi and they offered to refund and buy directly 5.49$ version instead. Which solved the problem. Awesome customer service!!

I homeschool both of my children and purchased this app years ago for my first child, she loved it. Now that my son is interested in learning letters and numbers he is enjoying it too. I do recommend.
Great game my four year old girl loves it. 4 stars because her unicorn sticker was removed for no reason.
Best learning apps ever designed and hope you continue making these apps.
Good educational game, know your children are learning with this app

I homeschool my kids, and use these apps instead of curriculum for lots of basic skills - $2 instead of $30-$100 to cover phonics, spelling, grammar (in versions for higher grades), math, thinking skills.... best deal I've found in quite a while, and way more fun for my ADHD girl than deskwork.  I have the paid versions for preschool thru 3rd grade.
Very happy with app. Very unhappy I was forced to re-buy the full version, and yet the free version said I already owned it.
